296
00:13:56,919 --> 00:13:58,879
It's your big day,

297
00:13:59,759 --> 00:14:00,919
but Prince Rui

298
00:14:01,120 --> 00:14:02,279
didn't even send a greeting.

299
00:14:02,639 --> 00:14:03,639
He's already off

300
00:14:03,679 --> 00:14:04,919
looking for Ling Chuchu.

301
00:14:05,639 --> 00:14:06,639
If word gets out,

302
00:14:07,399 --> 00:14:08,879
what will people say about you?

303
00:14:09,879 --> 00:14:11,320
As long as the PM's Mansion is safe,

304
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:12,840
I don't care

305
00:14:13,200 --> 00:14:13,799
what others say.

306
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:16,240
My Lady,

307
00:14:16,840 --> 00:14:18,600
you're the principal consort.

308
00:14:18,600 --> 00:14:19,559
Ling Chuchu

309
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:20,759
is just a concubine.

310
00:14:22,480 --> 00:14:23,080
She will

311
00:14:23,360 --> 00:14:24,919
take advantage of His Highness' favor

312
00:14:24,919 --> 00:14:25,879
to make things difficult for you.

313
00:14:26,480 --> 00:14:26,919
It's okay.

314
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:31,759
Bah!

315
00:14:32,399 --> 00:14:32,960
You shameless

316
00:14:33,200 --> 00:14:33,720
b*stards!

317
00:14:36,840 --> 00:14:37,600
I'll go out.

318
00:14:37,919 --> 00:14:38,559
Zhiyan, you go to bed first.

319
00:14:50,600 --> 00:14:52,039
Prime Minister Shen committed treason.

320
00:14:52,519 --> 00:14:53,840
After being discovered by me,

321
00:14:54,360 --> 00:14:55,399
he confessed and was executed.

322
00:15:12,759 --> 00:15:14,960
Didn't you miss your father and brother?

323
00:15:15,519 --> 00:15:17,000
Shall I take you home now?

324
00:15:17,559 --> 00:15:18,279
Go home.

325
00:15:18,919 --> 00:15:19,519
Go home.

326
00:15:20,039 --> 00:15:20,840
Okay.

327
00:15:41,879 --> 00:15:42,720
Chuchu,

328
00:15:43,159 --> 00:15:44,799
do I look like a puppy?

329
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:47,200
Your voice is quite similar.

330
00:15:47,679 --> 00:15:48,200
But

331
00:15:48,679 --> 00:15:49,600
puppies

332
00:15:50,000 --> 00:15:51,320
can't stand up.

333
00:15:57,360 --> 00:15:58,360
It fell again.

334
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:03,320
Sister Chuchu

335
00:16:03,440 --> 00:16:04,440
Didn't you promise me

336
00:16:04,720 --> 00:16:07,000
to take me home to see my brother and father?

337
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:07,720
Go away!

338
00:16:08,159 --> 00:16:08,879
What bad luck!

339
00:16:31,759 --> 00:16:32,399
Sir

340
00:16:33,559 --> 00:16:34,960
You haven't paid your bill yet.

341
00:16:39,480 --> 00:16:40,000
Sorry.

342
00:16:40,879 --> 00:16:42,360
I was in such a hurry.

343
00:16:42,840 --> 00:16:43,519
I forgot to bring money.

344
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:44,559
How about this?

345
00:16:44,799 --> 00:16:45,639
I'll write you a note.

346
00:16:45,919 --> 00:16:46,519
Tomorrow,

347
00:16:46,879 --> 00:16:47,639
you can go to the Prime Minister's Residence

348
00:16:48,759 --> 00:16:49,720
or Prince Rui's Mansion to get your money.

349
00:16:51,279 --> 00:16:52,320
You mean

350
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:53,960
I should go to Prince Rui's Mansion to collect money?

351
00:16:54,559 --> 00:16:55,240
Are you

352
00:16:55,720 --> 00:16:56,679
Princess Consort of Rui?

353
00:16:58,000 --> 00:16:58,519
Yes.

354
00:16:58,960 --> 00:16:59,399
I am.

355
00:16:59,440 --> 00:17:00,080
Bah!

356
00:17:00,600 --> 00:17:01,679
Everyone knows

357
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:03,399
that Prince Rui

358
00:17:03,720 --> 00:17:05,359
just married his wife today.

359
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:07,039
On their wedding night,

360
00:17:07,279 --> 00:17:07,960
you mean

361
00:17:08,160 --> 00:17:08,759
Princess Consort of Rui

362
00:17:08,839 --> 00:17:10,599
came to my tavern alone

363
00:17:10,599 --> 00:17:11,519
to drink?

364
00:17:12,000 --> 00:17:12,599
Even the devil wouldn't believe it.

365
00:17:12,839 --> 00:17:14,160
If you don't believe it,

366
00:17:14,559 --> 00:17:16,079
just go with me to the mansion.

367
00:17:16,200 --> 00:17:16,480
Let's go.

368
00:17:17,680 --> 00:17:18,759
Shut up.

369
00:17:19,480 --> 00:17:20,240
Pay me.

370
00:17:20,880 --> 00:17:21,359
Or

371
00:17:21,920 --> 00:17:23,759
I'll sell you to the brothel.

372
00:17:24,839 --> 00:17:25,160
Let me go.
